main_body:
Authorisation
The following products are authorised for the purposes of Article 4(2) and Article 16(2) of Regulation (EC) No 1829/2003, according to the conditions specified in this Decision:
(a) feed produced from BPS-25271-9 potato;
(b) foods containing, consisting of, or produced from BPS-25271-9 potato resulting from the adventitious or technically unavoidable presence of this GMO in a proportion no higher than 0,9 % of the food ingredients considered individually or food consisting of a single ingredient;
(c) feed containing or consisting of BPS-25271-9 potato resulting from the adventitious or technically unavoidable presence of this GMO in a proportion no higher than 0,9 % of the feed and of each feed of which it is composed.
